d-40af-897d-6c588e2696aa","execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2024-05-06T12:48:17.203586Z","iopub.execute_input":"2024-05-06T12:48:17.205158Z","iopub.status.idle":"2024-05-06T12:48:17.222959Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"### Obtendo $e$","metadata":{"id":"NHbXlLk-G3Hn"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"e <- z * sigma\ne","metadata":{"id":"gAfakih5G3Ho","outputId":"48958fa3-2cf8-4bc5-dfc3-0fb925798b38","execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2024-05-06T12:48:18.421711Z","iopub.execute_input":"2024-05-06T12:48:18.423331Z","iopub.status.idle":"2024-05-06T12:48:18.441486Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"### Solução 1 - Calculando o intervalo de confiança para a média","metadata":{"id":"sx1QTfNrG3Hq"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"intervalo <- c(\n    media_amostral - e,\n    media_amostral + e\n)\nintervalo","metadata":{"id":"NlJCcPZnG3Hq","outputId":"09cee323-103e-4832-c23f-97daf4b9929f","execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2024-05-06T12:48:20.223974Z","iopub.execute_input":"2024-05-06T12:48:20.225612Z","iopub.status.idle":"2024-05-06T12:48:20.244502Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"### Solução 2 - Calculando o intervalo de confiança para a média\n\n#### <font color=red>Documentações:\n\n- [**MeanCI**](https://www.rdocumentation.org/packages/DescTools/versions/0.99.30/topics/MeanCI)","metadata":{"id":"DkFJL7fcG3Ht"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"#### Instalação do pacote DescTools\n\nhttps://cran.r-project.org","metadata":{}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"install.packages('DescTools')\n\n# OU\n\npackageurl <- \"https://cran.r-project.org/src/contrib/Archive/DescTools/DescTools_0.99.30.tar.gz\"\ninstall.packages(packageurl, repos=NULL, type=\"source\")","metadata":{"scrolled":true,"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2024-05-06T12:48:48.179680Z","iopub.execute_input":"2024-05-06T12:48:48.181607Z","iopub.status.idle":"2024-05-06T12:49:54.566988Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"code","source":"library(DescTools)","metadata":{"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2024-05-06T12:50:31.908921Z","iopub.execute_input":"2024-05-06T12:50:31.910767Z","iopub.status.idle":"2024-05-06T12:50:31.925946Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"code","source":"MeanCI(x = 5050, sd = sigma, type = 'norm', conf.level = 0.95, sides = 'two.sided')","metadata":{"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2024-05-06T12:50:35.002207Z","iopub.execute_input":"2024-05-06T12:50:35.004161Z","iopub.status.idle":"2024-05-06T12:50:35.027767Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"code","source":"mean(dados$Idade) - (z * (sd(dados$Idade) / sqrt(nrow(dados))))\nmean(dados$Idade) + (z * (sd(dados$Idade) / sqrt(nrow(dados))))","metadata":{"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2024-05-06T12:50:37.241446Z","iopub.execute_input":"2024-05-06T12:50:37.243598Z","iopub.status.idle":"2024-05-06T12:50:37.276788Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"code","source":"sigma <- sd(dados$Idade) / sqrt(nrow(dados))","metadata":{"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2024-05-06T12:50:39.078584Z","iopub.execute_input":"2024-05-06T12:50:39.080714Z","iopub.status.idle":"2024-05-06T12:50:39.099162Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"code","source":"MeanCI(x = mean(dados$Idade), sd = sigma, type = 'norm', conf.level = 0.95, sides = 'two.sided')","metadata":{"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2024-05-06T12:50:41.826260Z","iopub.execute_input":"2024-05-06T12:50:41.828270Z","iopub.status.idle":"2024-05-06T12:50:41.850556Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"# <font color=green>5 CÁLCULO DO TAMANHO DA AMOSTRA</font>\n***","metadata":{"id":"aF9jAC6yG3Gl"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"## <font color='red'>Problema </font>","metadata":{"id":"BwiygaNqnjrr"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"Estamos estudando o rendimento mensal dos chefes de domicílios no Brasil. Nosso supervisor determinou que o **erro máximo em relação a média seja de R$\\$$ 100,00**. Sabemos que o **desvio padrão populacional** deste grupo de trabalhadores é de **R$\\$$ 3.323,39**. Para um **nível de confiança de 95%**, qual deve ser o tamanho da amostra de nosso estudo?","metadata":{"id":"a7RjjVVUnlI3"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"## <font color=green>5.1 Variáveis quantitativas e população infinita</font>\n***","metadata":{"id":"za2sGJt6G3Gm"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"# $$e = z \\frac{\\sigma}{\\sqrt{n}}$$","metadata":{"id":"3wqMjJWR5sVq"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"#### Com desvio padrão conhecido\n\n## $$n = \\left(z\\frac{\\sigma}{e}\\right)^2$$\n\n#### Com desvio padrão desconhecido\n\n## $$n = \\left(z\\frac{s}{e}\\right)^2$$\n\nOnde:\n\n$z$ = variável normal padronizada\n\n$\\sigma$ = desvio padrão populacional\n\n$s$ = desvio padrão amostral\n\n$e$ = erro inferencial","metadata":{"id":"X1AxpKtIG3Gn"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"### <font color='red'>Observações</font>\n\n1. O desvio padrão ($\\sigma$ ou $s$) e o erro ($e$) devem estar na mesma unidade de medida.\n\n2. Quando o erro ($e$) for representado em termos percentuais, deve ser interpretado como um percentual relacionado à média.","metadata":{"id":"T0fysCyDG3Gn"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"## <font color='blue'>Exemplo: Rendimento médio</font>","metadata":{"id":"WHYBTaupG3Gn"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"Estamos estudando o rendimento mensal dos chefes de domicílios no Brasil. Nosso supervisor determinou que o **erro máximo em relação a média seja de R$\\$$ 100,00**. Sabemos que o **desvio padrão populacional** deste grupo de trabalhadores é de **R$\\$$ 3.323,39**. Para um **nível de confiança de 95%**, qual deve ser o tamanho da amostra de nosso estudo?","metadata":{"id":"dcdzo7EgG3Go"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"0.95 / 2","metadata":{"id":"XtJ5I_kaKDN3","outputId":"a519e330-ddf0-492c-f42d-5cef36fed4c9","execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2024-05-06T12:50:45.372990Z","iopub.execute_input":"2024-05-06T12:50:45.375026Z","iopub.status.idle":"2024-05-06T12:50:45.414538Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"code","source":"0.5 + (0.95 / 2)","metadata":{"id":"-4TLCgNLKC95","outputId":"19f3b7af-ff33-4db4-c675-c62b5088137e","execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2024-05-06T12:50:46.925049Z","iopub.execute_input":"2024-05-06T12:50:46.926629Z","iopub.status.idle":"2024-05-06T12:50:46.946680Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"code","source":"z <- qnorm(0.975)\nz","metadata":{"id":"7XDT12I4ViYN","outputId":"a0af8729-80a8-4b33-b307-96d144c83029","execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2024-05-06T12:50:48.698443Z","iopub.execute_input":"2024-05-06T12:50:48.700082Z","iopub.status.idle":"2024-05-06T12:50:48.719285Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"### Obtendo $\\sigma$","metadata":{"id":"6uCkW4KlG3Gr"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"sigma <- 3323.39\nsigma","metadata":{"id":"1RmtZfj-G3Gr","outputId":"d3e77bf1-b933-4ade-846f-95e25f4e1d6e","execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2024-05-06T12:50:50.313557Z","iopub.execute_input":"2024-05-06T12:50:50.315074Z","iopub.status.idle":"2024-05-06T12:50:50.331986Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"### Obtendo $e$","metadata":{"id":"Cl39PIZ2G3Gt"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"e <- 100\ne","metadata":{"id":"NTRMt2gWG3Gt","outputId":"f7d7ae3f-7e33-41cc-a11a-5b09de70cc2c","execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2024-05-06T12:50:51.934054Z","iopub.execute_input":"2024-05-06T12:50:51.935771Z","iopub.status.idle":"2024-05-06T12:50:51.953438Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"### Obtendo $n$","metadata":{"id":"OlAX3Gj6G3Gv"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"n <- (z * (sigma / e)) ** 2\nround(n)","metadata":{"id":"0MjluwHPG3Gv","outputId":"8f74510a-4f4b-4129-d3c3-d31be24567fa","scrolled":true,"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2024-05-06T12:50:54.037322Z","iopub.execute_input":"2024-05-06T12:50:54.039454Z","iopub.status.idle":"2024-05-06T12:50:54.060664Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"---","metadata":{"id":"MjP0xsqyTyNO"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"## <font color='red'>Problema</font>","metadata":{"id":"dx2vyLC-TyNP"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"Em um lote de **10.000 latas** de refrigerante foi realizada uma amostra aleatória simples de **100 latas** e foi obtido o **desvio padrão amostral do conteúdo das latas igual a 12 ml**. O fabricante estipula um **erro máximo sobre a média populacional de apenas 5 ml**. Para garantir um **nível de confiança de 95%** qual o tamanho de amostra deve ser selecionado para este estudo?","metadata":{"id":"uzK2fAOFTyNP"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"## <font color=green>5.2 Variáveis quantitativas e população finita</font>\n***","metadata":{"id":"FlAz5kycTyNQ"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"#### Com desvio padrão conhecido\n\n## $$n = \\frac{z^2 \\sigma^2 N}{z^2 \\sigma^2 + e^2(N-1)}$$\n\n#### Com desvio padrão desconhecido\n\n## $$n = \\frac{z^2 s^2 N}{z^2 s^2 + e^2(N-1)}$$\n\nOnde:\n\n$N$ = tamanho da população\n\n$z$ = variável normal padronizada\n\n$\\sigma$ = desvio padrão populacional\n\n$s$ = desvio padrão amostral\n\n$e$ = erro inferencial","metadata":{"id":"UOe02McSTyNR"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"## <font color='blue'>Exemplo: Indústria de refrigerantes</font>","metadata":{"id":"cUELtYTKTyNS"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"Em um lote de **10.000 latas** de refrigerante foi realizada uma amostra aleatória simples de **100 latas** e foi obtido o **desvio padrão amostral do conteúdo das latas igual a 12 ml**. O fabricante estipula um **erro máximo sobre a média populacional de apenas 5 ml**. Para garantir um **nível de confiança de 95%** qual o tamanho de amostra deve ser selecionado para este estudo?","metadata":{"id":"upv1mM7fTyNS"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"### Obtendo $N$","metadata":{"id":"_y3-3VIBTyNS"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"N <- 10000\nN","metadata":{"id":"gXWn9zTETyNS","outputId":"4daa26ff-4a96-47fb-9f0e-53a4390d701e","execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2024-05-06T12:50:57.121137Z","iopub.execute_input":"2024-05-06T12:50:57.122719Z","iopub.status.idle":"2024-05-06T12:50:57.141733Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"### Obtendo $z$","metadata":{"id":"xCgZ1JSjTyNT"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"z <- qnorm((0.5 + (0.95 / 2)))\nz","metadata":{"id":"ZUs9aYJRTyNT","outputId":"02560c9f-57ee-41c7-cdf4-5fd382365a74","execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2024-05-06T12:50:58.476901Z","iopub.execute_input":"2024-05-06T12:50:58.478569Z","iopub.status.idle":"2024-05-06T12:50:58.498083Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"### Obtendo $s$","metadata":{"id":"KCnigJd8TyNU"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"s <- 12\ns","metadata":{"id":"fKqFI_TZTyNU","outputId":"68a9ee2f-428a-4d18-9148-f33704968fb7","execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2024-05-06T12:51:00.387065Z","iopub.execute_input":"2024-05-06T12:51:00.388845Z","iopub.status.idle":"2024-05-06T12:51:00.408404Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"### Obtendo $e$","metadata":{"id":"K9gDEIUdTyNX"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"e <- 5\ne","metadata":{"id":"hyhJ3MQKTyNX","outputId":"2849bd05-6c70-4d97-980d-67e140f27850","execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2024-05-06T12:51:01.875910Z","iopub.execute_input":"2024-05-06T12:51:01.877616Z","iopub.status.idle":"2024-05-06T12:51:01.899713Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":null,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"### Obtendo $n$\n\n## $$n = \\frac{z^2 s^2 N}{z^2 s^2 + e^2(N-1)}$$","metadata":{"id":"Dsm3bg9gTyNX"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"n <- ((z ** 2) * (s ** 2) * (N)) / (((z ** 2) * (s ** 2)) + ((e ** 2) * (N - 1)))\nround(n)","metadata":{"id":"0XxWfaPdTyNY","outputId":"8494180f-9149-419f-dee9-f02ec3e81b93","scrolled":true,"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2024-05-06T13:05:16.248041Z","iopub.execute_input":"2024-05-06T13:05:16.249711Z","iopub.status.idle":"2024-05-06T13:05:16.281184Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":105,"outputs":[{"output_type":"display_data","data":{"text/html":"6","text/markdown":"6","text/latex":"6","text/plain":"[1] 6"},"metadata":{}}]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"# <font color=green>6 FIXANDO O CONTEÚDO</font>\n***","metadata":{"id":"XNH7CMglG3Hv"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"## <font color='blue'>Exemplo: Rendimento médio</font>","metadata":{"id":"iRYqVAxuG3Hv"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"Estamos estudando o **rendimento mensal dos chefes de domicílios com renda até R$\\$$ 5.000,00 no Brasil**. Nosso supervisor determinou que o **erro máximo em relação a média seja de R$\\$$ 10,00**. Sabemos que o **desvio padrão populacional** deste grupo de trabalhadores é de **R$\\$$ 1.082,79** e que a **média populacional** é de **R$\\$$ 1.426,54**. Para um **nível de confiança de 95%**, qual deve ser o tamanho da amostra de nosso estudo? Qual o intervalo de confiança para a média considerando o tamanho de amostra obtido?","metadata":{"id":"ggloHI5sG3Hw"}},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"### Construindo o dataset conforme especificado pelo problema","metadata":{"id":"JZDvLD-NG3Hw"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"renda_5000 <- dados[dados$Renda <= 5000, ]","metadata":{"id":"qlnYQeaKG3Hw","execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2024-05-06T13:05:09.382770Z","iopub.execute_input":"2024-05-06T13:05:09.384508Z","iopub.status.idle":"2024-05-06T13:05:09.412703Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":102,"outputs":[]},{"cell_type":"code","source":"sigma <- sd(renda_5000$Renda)\nsigma","metadata":{"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2024-05-06T13:05:11.063937Z","iopub.execute_input":"2024-05-06T13:05:11.065646Z","iopub.status.idle":"2024-05-06T13:05:11.085282Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":103,"outputs":[{"output_type":"display_data","data":{"text/html":"1082.79454903068","text/markdown":"1082.79454903068","text/latex":"1082.79454903068","text/plain":"[1] 1082.795"},"metadata":{}}]},{"cell_type":"code","source":"media <- mean(renda_5000$Renda)\nmedia","metadata":{"id":"VKuxbygIG3Hy","outputId":"98078826-90d1-488e-b11d-cf4e6f5bdc3c","execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2024-05-06T13:05:12.756809Z","iopub.execute_input":"2024-05-06T13:05:12.758398Z","iopub.status.idle":"2024-05-06T13:05:12.776676Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":104,"outputs":[{"output_type":"display_data","data":{"text/html":"1426.53721449472","text/markdown":"1426.53721449472","text/latex":"1426.53721449472","text/plain":"[1] 1426.537"},"metadata":{}}]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"### Calculando o tamanho da amostra","metadata":{"id":"F33TdkXdG3H2"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"z <- qnorm(.975)\ne <- 10\nn <- (z * (sigma / e)) ** 2\nround(n)","metadata":{"id":"sWIvnmygG3H2","outputId":"42b7f8db-3a43-4e5f-f61a-9000e4e5e94b","execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2024-05-06T13:05:27.313901Z","iopub.execute_input":"2024-05-06T13:05:27.315821Z","iopub.status.idle":"2024-05-06T13:05:27.338346Z"},"trusted":true},"execution_count":106,"outputs":[{"output_type":"display_data","data":{"text/html":"45039","text/markdown":"45039","text/latex":"45039","text/plain":"[1] 45039"},"metadata":{}}]},{"cell_type":"markdown","source":"### Calculando o intervalo de confiança para a média","metadata":{"id":"xRN_gmmLG3H6"}},{"cell_type":"code","source":"limite_inferior <- mean(renda_5000$Renda) - (z * (sd(renda_5000$Renda) / sqrt(n)))\nlimite_superior <- mean(renda_5000$Renda) + (z * (sd(renda_5000$Renda) / sqrt(n)))","metadata":{"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2024-05-06T13:05:29.456178Z","iopub.execute_input":"2024-05-06T13: